location.fullValue: Blue Spruce Bonus Room 2 Plus Plan, Delmer Lakes North

data.description: Beautiful Builder Model Home resale with 3 Bed, 2.1 Bath, 2 Living, 1 office and 3 car garage on the greenbelt in Stonebriar. Beautiful views the moment you walk in the front door. Gourmet kitchen with generous cabinets and countertops. (granite) Long island with sink, nice sized pantry and Stainless appliances including the refrigerator. Primary Suite with walk-in shower, separate whirlpool bath and spacious walk-in closet with a built-in armoire. Laundry has extra cabinets, stone counter top and the washer & dryer stay. Two fireplaces one inside and one under the covered patio with incredible views. HOA includes a pool and fishing pond.Property has been well maintained. Easy access to grocery stores, medical, restaurants and  gyms.
